      "quote": "60.0 percent was transferred to the Senior Services Trust Fund, 15.3 percent was transferred to the State Medicaid Match Fund— SRS, 9.7 percent was transferred to the State Medicaid Match Fund— Department on Aging, 10.0 percent was transferred to the Long-Term Care Loan and Grant Fund, and 5.0 percent was transferred to the HCBS Programs Fund.",
